    • bootShell.ts
      function bootShell(bootHTML: string, uiFrameReadyCallback: Function) {

  var bootStyle = elem(
    'style',
    'iframe.ui{display:none;} ' +
    'iframe.boot{display:block;}',
    document.body);

  var bootIFR = createFrame('boot', function bootFrameReady(bootFrame) {

    bootFrame.global.require = require;

    bootFrame.global.eval(
      elem + '\n' + setText + '\n' + onEvent + '\n' + offEvent + '\n' + dateNow + '\n' +
      ' //# sourceURL=inlines.js');

    if (bootFrame.document.open) bootFrame.document.open();
    bootFrame.document.write(bootHTML);
    if (bootFrame.document.close) bootFrame.document.close();

  });

  onEvent(window, 'load', function onloadCompleted() {
    var uiFrame = createFrame('ui', (uiDoc, uiGobal, uiFrame) => {
      document.body.removeChild(bootIFR);
      uiFrameReadyCallback(uiDoc, uiGobal, uiFrame);
      document.body.removeChild(bootStyle);
    });
  });

  function require(module) {
    if (module === 'boot') {
      return {
        document: document,
        window: window
      };
    }
  }

}

    • createFrame.ts
      function createFrame(className: string): { global: any; document: Document; iframe: HTMLIFrameElement; } {

  var frm = <HTMLIFrameElement>elem('iframe', { className: className });
  frm.src = 'about:blank';
  document.body.appendChild(frm);

  if (frm.contentWindow && frm.contentWindow.document && frm.contentWindow.document !== document)
    return { global: frm.contentWindow, document: frm.contentWindow.document, iframe: frm };

  if (frm.document && frm.document !== document && (<Window><any>frm).alert)
    return { global: frm, document: frm.document, iframe: frm };

}

    • elem.ts
      function elem(
  tag: string | HTMLElement,
  style?: string | { [name: string]: any; },
  parent?: Element): HTMLElement {

  var e = (<HTMLElement>tag).tagName ? tag : this.document.createElement(tag);

  if (!style && parent.tagName) {
    parent = <any>style;
    style = null;
  }

  if (style) {
    if (typeof style === 'string') {
      setText(e, style);
    }
    else {
      for (var k in style) if (style.hasOwnProperty(k)) {
        if (k === 'text') {
          setText(e, style[k]);
        }
        else if (k === 'className') {
          e.className = style[k];
        }
        else {
          try {
            e.style[k] = style[k];
          }
          catch (err) {
            if (typeof console !== 'undefined' && typeof console.error === 'function')
              console.error(err);
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  if (parent)
    parent.appendChild(e);

  return e;
}
    • onoff.ts
      function onEvent(
  e: HTMLElement | Element | Window,
   eventName: string,
   handler: (e: Event) => void) {
  if (e.addEventListener)
    e.addEventListener(eventName, handler, false);
  else if ((<HTMLElement>e).attachEvent)
    (<HTMLElement>e).attachEvent('on'+eventName, handler);
  else if ('on'+eventName in e)
    e['on'+eventName] = handler;
  else if (typeof console !== 'undefined' && typeof console.warn === 'function')
    console.warn('Neither addEventListener nor attachEvent nor on'+eventName+' on '+e+' '+(<HTMLElement>e).tagName+'.');
}

function offEvent(
  e: HTMLElement | Element | Window,
   eventName: string,
   handler: (e: Event) => void) {
  if (e.addEventListener)
    e.addEventListener(eventName, handler, false);
  else if ((<HTMLElement>e).attachEvent)
    (<HTMLElement>e).attachEvent('on' + eventName, handler);
  else if ('on' + eventName in e)
    e['on' + eventName] = handler;
  else if (typeof console !== 'undefined' && typeof console.warn === 'function')
    console.warn('Neither addEventListener nor attachEvent nor on' + eventName + ' on ' + e + ' ' + (<HTMLElement>e).tagName + '.');
}
    • setText.ts
      function setText(e: HTMLElement, text: string) {
  if (!/^BODY$/i.test(e.tagName) && 'text' in e)
    (<any>e).text = text;
  else if ('textContent' in e)
    e.textContent = text;
  else if ('innerText' in e)
    e.innerText = text;
  else if ('innerHTML' in e)
    e.innerHTML = text;
  else if (typeof console !== 'undefined' && typeof console.error === 'function')
    console.error('Cannot neither text nor textContent nor innerText nor innerHTML is present on element ' + e + ' ' + e.tagName + '.');
}

    • IFrameModuleLoader.ts
      module mi.mods {

  export class IFrameModuleLoader {

    constructor(private _hostDocument = document) {
    }

    loadModule(path: string, jsCode: string): any {
      var ff = openIFrame(this._hostDocument);
      prepareIFrame(ff.iframe, ff.document);

      (<any>ff.global).require = (name) => this.require(name);

      var wrappedCode = 'var exports = {}; (function(window, document, alert){' + jsCode + '})() //# sourceURL=' + path;

      var script = ff.document.createElement('script');
      if ('text' in script) {
        script.text = wrappedCode;
      }
      else {
        script.innerHTML = wrappedCode;
      }
      ff.document.body.appendChild(script);
      while (ff.document.body.children.length)
        ff.document.body.removeChild(ff.document.body.children[0]);

      return (<any>ff.global).exports;
    }

    require(name: string): any {
      if (name == 'fs')
        return {
          readFileSync: () => { }
        };
    }

  }

  function prepareIFrame(iframe: HTMLIFrameElement, document: Document) {
    document.open();
    document.write('<body><script>var window = null; var document = null; var top = null; var parent = null; var exports = {};</' + 'script></body>');
    document.close();
    document.body.removeChild(document.scripts[0]);
  }

  function openIFrame(document: Document) {
    var iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
    iframe.src = 'about:blank';
    //(<any>iframe).srcdoc = '';
    iframe.setAttribute('sandbox', 'allow-same-origin allow-scripts');
    iframe.style.display = 'none';
    document.body.appendChild(iframe);

    var pollUntil = dateNow();
    do {
      if (iframe.contentWindow && iframe.contentWindow.document && iframe.contentWindow.document !== document)
        return { iframe, global: iframe.contentWindow, document: iframe.contentWindow.document };
      if (iframe.document && iframe.document !== document)
        return { iframe, global: <Window>(<any>document).window, document: iframe.document };


    } while (dateNow() < pollUntil);

    throw new Error('Cannot load and access an empty document in a hidden IFRAME.');
  }

}

      function loadHeadlessMod(
  options: {
    scope?: { [name: string]: any; };
    eval: string;
   	path?: string;
  }): void {

  var ff = createFrame(null, frame => {
    document.body.removeChild(frame.iframe);

    var allowGlobals = { setTimeout: 1, setInterval: 1, clearTimeout: 1, clearInterval: 1 };

    var exportsInScope = options.scope && 'exports' in options.scope;
    var evalArgNames: string[] = exportsInScope ? [] : ['exports'];
    var evalArgs: any[] = exportsInScope ? [] : [{}];
    if (options.scope) {
      for (var k in options.scope) if (options.scope.hasOwnProperty(k)) {
        evalArgNames.push(k);
        evalArgs.push(options.scope[k]);
      }
    }

    for (var k in frame.global) {
      if (options.scope && options.scope.hasOwnProperty(k)) continue;
      if (allowGlobals.hasOwnProperty(k)) continue;
      evalArgNames.push(k);
    }

    evalArgNames.push(
      options.path ? options.eval + '\nreturn exports; //# sourceURL=' + options.path : options.eval);

    var evalFn = frame.global.Function.call(frame.global, evalArgNames);

    var modExports = evalFn.call(frame.global, evalArgs);
  });


  function prepareIFrame(iframe: HTMLIFrameElement, document: Document) {
    document.open();
    document.write('<body><script>var window = null; var document = null; var top = null; var parent = null; var exports = {};</' + 'script></body>');
    document.close();
    document.body.removeChild(document.scripts[0]);
  }

  function openIFrame(document: Document) {
    var iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
    iframe.src = 'about:blank';
    //(<any>iframe).srcdoc = '';
    iframe.setAttribute('sandbox', 'allow-same-origin allow-scripts');
    iframe.style.display = 'none';
    document.body.appendChild(iframe);

    var pollUntil = dateNow();
    do {
      if (iframe.contentWindow && iframe.contentWindow.document && iframe.contentWindow.document !== document)
        return { iframe, global: iframe.contentWindow, document: iframe.contentWindow.document };
      if (iframe.document && iframe.document !== document)
        return { iframe, global: <Window>(<any>document).window, document: iframe.document };


    } while (dateNow() < pollUntil);

    throw new Error('Cannot load and access an empty document in a hidden IFRAME.');
  }

}

      function loadUIMod(
  options: {
    className?: string;
    scope?: { [name: string]: any; };
   	html: string;
  }) {

  var frame = createFrame(options.className);
  if (options.scope) {
    for (var k in options.scope) if (options.scope.hasOwnProperty(k)) {
      frame.global[k] = options.scope[k];
    }
  }

  if (frame.document.open) frame.document.open();
    frame.document.write(options.html);
  if (frame.document.close) frame.document.close();

  return frame;

}
